OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775823082
OL,3,C'Prolonged and painful deaths' RSPCA
OL,4,Cappeal after crate of dead pigeons
OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FThe RSPCA is investigating after a
OL,8,Fcrate of 25 dead pigeons was found by
OL,9,Fa bin in Chipping Norton in
OL,10,FOxfordshire.
OL,12,FThe charity was made aware of the
OL,13,Fdiscovery on West Street, by the
OL,14,Fturning for The Green, at 9.20am on 1
OL,15,FApril.
OL,17,FIt says all the birds appeared to have
OL,18,Fbeen shot with an air gun - and
OL,19,Fsuffered a prolonged and painful death.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
