OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775823082
OL,3,C'Prolonged and painful deaths' RSPCA
OL,4,Cappeal after crate of dead pigeons
OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,8,Fcontact the charity.
OL,10,FRSPCA inspector Prisca Giddens, who is
OL,11,Finvestigating for the animal charity,
OL,12,Fsaid: "The pigeons all have injuries
OL,13,Fconsistent with being shot by an air
OL,14,Fgun, many have wounds from the
OL,15,Fpellets, broken wings, and blood from
OL,16,Ftheir mouths.
OL,18,FA number have an obvious neck break,
OL,19,Fsuggesting they weren't killed
OL,20,Finstantly by the pellets, but were
OL,21,Flater killed manually.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775823082
OL,3,C'Prolonged and painful deaths' RSPCA
OL,4,Cappeal after crate of dead pigeons
OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,F"These birds suffered prolonged and
OL,8,Fpainful deaths and their bodies were
OL,9,Fthen left in a public place in the
OL,10,Ftown centre, close to a school.
OL,12,F"We're asking anyone with information
OL,13,Fcontact me on our inspectorate appeal
OL,14,Fline on 0300 123 8018, quoting
OL,15,Freference 01767079."
OL,17,FThe RSPCA said it receives nearly
OL,18,F1,000 calls each year about air
OL,19,Fweapons being used to target animals.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1775823082
OL,3,C'Prolonged and painful deaths' RSPCA
OL,4,Cappeal after crate of dead pigeons
OL,5,Cfound
OL,7,FThe charity is asking for stricter
OL,8,Flicensing, mandatory safety training,
OL,9,Fand better education on current laws
OL,10,Fto prevent deliberate animal cruelty.
OL,12,FPrisca added: "Cats and wildlife are
OL,13,Fthe animals most susceptible to being
OL,14,Fshot simply because they are out in
OL,15,Fthe open with no-one to protect them.
OL,17,F"Sadly, air weapon attacks are not
OL,18,Frare and the injuries caused can be
OL,19,Fhorrific and often fatal."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
